  "summary": {
    "as": "Introduced in Senate",
    "asOf": "2021-03-16",
    "date": "2021-07-01T01:39:17Z",
    "text": "Executive Branch Emissions Transparency Act\n\nThis bill requires the Office of Management and Budget to establish and maintain a publicly accessible and searchable database of fossil fuel-powered travel by the President, the Vice President, and political appointees where such travel is on official business or paid for by a third party if the individual is appearing in their official capacity.\n\nThe bill makes an exception where publishing on the database could be deemed a national security risk."
